These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
House: cape-cod, art-deco, victorian, colonial
1. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the cape-cod house##6
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the colonial house##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the victorian house##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
6. the cape-cod house is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | colonial | cape-cod | victorian | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, november, january
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
4. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | august  | november    | may | january    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, puzzles, card-games
1. the person drinking water is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | puzzles | card-games | skydiving | video-games  |

