.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, snake
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, 7up
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the person drinking 7up is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake     | goldfish |
| Transport   | hot-chocolate     | soy-milk    | almond-milk | 7up    |

