.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
House: modern, futuristic, victorian, ranch-style
1. the modern house is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is not the futuristic house##6
3. the modern house is on the far right##1
4. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
5. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
7. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
9. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy    | disaster  | thriller   |
| Nationality   | victorian  | ranch-style | futuristic | modern |

