.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, trike, motorbike
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, gospel, reggae
1. the fan gospel is on the left or right of the fan country##3
2. the fan gospel is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
3. the person driving the boat is the fan d&b##1
4. the fan country is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
5. the fan gospel is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan country##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | motorbike | snowmobile     | trike | boat |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | country | reggae      | d&b         |

