.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
City: hamburg, prague, boston, berlin
1. the person traveling to hamburg is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person traveling to berlin##6
6. the person traveling to prague is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | hamburg     | berlin | prague | boston |

