.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, apricot, pear, pomegranate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
3. the fan indie is not the person eating pear##6
4. the person eating apricot is between the fan pop and the person eating pear##2
5. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person eating spinach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | pear | apricot    | spinach | pomegranate |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

