.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, banana, lettuce, pomegranate
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, scientist, project-manager, software-developer
1. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
2. the person eating banana is not the scientist##6
3. the person eating asparagus is the software-developer##1
4. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
5. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating banana and the entrepreneur##2
6. the person eating banana is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate | banana      | asparagus | lettuce   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientist     | project-manager | software-developer   | entrepreneur |

