5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person driving the boat and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person driving the boat is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
