4. the owner of the mouse is not the person eating corn##6
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the person eating corn and the person eating avocado##2
6. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating corn##1
8. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | avocado | pumpkin | corn | papaya |
| Pet     | lizard  | fish      | chinchilla  | mouse       |

